reviews.text: The service is great here! I came here with my 5 month old and ordered a strawberry shortcake and Americano. I had a few bites of the cake but had to leave with baby to the nursing room to feed and change him. I told the waiter to watch the table for me. When I came back the waiter offered to change a new piece of cake and coffee for me. Very nice cake and great experience. The waiters are all very polite and professional! Highly recommend this place for a nice afternoon tea break

The cakes and crepes are delicious but a little bit sweet. The price is reasonable. But the choices and quantity of cake and crepe offered daily are not enough, therefore, you have to go earlier if you want to taste your favourite one.
The signature mille crepes is very nice, soft and tasty,  not too sweet

Had lunch set there yesterday. Food quality is just average, except for the cake berry berry short cake for dessert, which is good living up to Lady M's reputation. Setting is typical Lady M. Service is ok but not impressive. Not as good as the one on Orchard Road, Singapore.

This place looks very royal and a good place for tea
Sometimes the queue will be long and the waiting time is a bit long
Overall the shop is good

reviews.text: This is a trendy shopping area located conveniently in Causeway Bay. There's a collection of fancy boutiques & clothing stores from various designer labels. The products are pretty high-end, meaning they could be pricier than the average store. Nonetheless, everything feels so glamorous and fashionable. This shopping area should appeal to a young demographic for sure.
Shop staff is friendly introducing the brand and they have nice product designs at KLASSE14 shop.
Small but nicely set up mall.  With Logon & Starbuck on 1st floor, I can spend a whole afternoon here. Clean washrooms on ground level. Convenient for visitors.
It has very good brands that you can't find commonly
Easy to get to & meet up with friends for a light bite & drinks. Really quaint & a nice variety to choose from. Not overly crowded too. A nice mix of eclectic groups of people and visitors.

result.formatted_address: G/F, 1-3 Cleveland St, Causeway Bay, 香港
result.name: Lady M Causeway Bay

reviews.text:
小排隊一下⋯⋯
兩人點了四片蛋糕真的太多了⋯⋯

由前菜、主菜、飲品到蛋糕均可自由配搭，蛋糕更是沒有限制，也不需額外加錢，真的很划算！午餐只限平日供應！

法國玫瑰鮮奶茶 (+$8)
顏值爆表，鋪滿了浪漫迷人的玫瑰花瓣，入口香醇順口，每一口都滲透着淡雅花香，滋味無窮。

冷天使麵伴溫泉蛋
幼身的天使麵掛滿黑松露蕎麥麵醬汁，再將富有芳郁蛋香的溫泉蛋拌勻一起吃，非常清新，好吃得停不下嘴。以天使麵代替冷麵/蕎麥麵這個配搭新穎又美味，為味蕾帶來新的驚喜！

牛油果炒蛋漢堡
單看賣相已經流口水！鬆軟的牛油軟包夾着熟透的牛油果、嫩滑炒蛋、自家製焦糖洋蔥和辣味蛋黃醬，甜甜辣辣，口感和味道豐富，滋味妙不可言。

玫瑰千層蛋糕
如此嬌艷動人的粉紅色外型，充滿了少女心和浪漫情懷。質感香軟幼滑，每一口都洋溢玫瑰香氣，口感細膩，但味道偏甜。

伯爵茶千層蛋糕
每片透薄細緻的班戟蛋皮之間均勻地塗上茶香芳郁的伯爵茶忌廉，厚薄一致沒有絲毫分差，十分精緻且口感豐富。柔滑的伯爵茶忌廉，幽香怡人，甜而不膩。

The service is great here! I came here with my 5 month old and ordered a strawberry shortcake and Americano. I had a few bites of the cake but had to leave with baby to the nursing room to feed and change him. I told the waiter to watch the table for me. When I came back the waiter offered to change a new piece of cake and coffee for me. Very nice cake and great experience. The waiters are all very polite and professional! Highly recommend this place for a nice afternoon tea break
